This is the build environment used to make Waterfox.
To create a 64-Bit build, execute the batch file start-shell-icc14-msvc2010-x64.bat.
Navigate to the Waterfox root directory and run ./mach build to get started!

Requirements:
The following is needed to build Waterfox successfully:
- Intel's C++ Compiler 13 Service Pack 1 Update 4
- Microsoft Visual Studio 2010 Service Pack 1
- DirectX SDK (June 2010)
- Windows 8.1 SDK